name: TEZONAZACA #3
description:
I inspired this character from “Nazca decapitator pot” ; The Nazca civilization was at its height from around 200 BCE to 650 CE..The Nazca mummified their dead, dressing them in magnificent textiles woven from llama, alpaca, and vicuña wool. They also produced pottery decorated with motifs of animals and supernatural beings. I bring the character in TEZOS life and called it “TEZONAZCA”. Each TEZONAZCA is unique and generated by combining different properties with varying rarities categories (Backgrounds, Skin, Face, Eyes, Mouth, earing, Hair and hat,…).
